/**
 * NewtonTool - Symbolic Math API Tool
 * 
 * Perform symbolic mathematics operations using Newton API.
 * API: https://newton.now.sh
 * 
 * Use cases:
 * - "หาอนุพันธ์ของ x^2 + 3x" → derive
 * - "simplify (x+1)(x-1)" → simplify
 * - "integrate x^2" → integrate
